                        a.information-main__link.orddev-main__link(href="#payment") ОПЛАТА
                        a.information-main__link.orddev-main__link(href="#delivery") ДОСТАВКА
                        a.information-main__link.orddev-main__link(href="#pickup") САМОВЫВОЗ
